By KIRSTEN LEE SWARTZ 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An 18-year-old Ventura man was killed in a car accident Friday when another 
vehicle struck him on the driver's side as he was making a left-hand turn in an 
intersection, Ventura police said. 
</P>
<P>
The man died of multiple injuries at 3 p.m. in the Ventura County Medical 
Center's operating room, Deputy Coroner Mitch Breese said. 
</P>
