Theater in New York, where she starred in "The House of Flowers." Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, Performer Pearl Bailey in 1987. United Press International; 
Photo, Disciplinary problems have decreased dramatically at Principal Robert 
Pipkin's revitalized Prospect Middle School in the Pittsburgh system. BILL 
METZGER / For The Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
