<HEADLINE>
<P>
LOS ALAMITOS SATELLITE WAGERING SUNDAY IS FREE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Los Alamitos Racing Assn. will begin satellite wagering from Del Mar on 
Sunday continuing through the end of the Del Mar thoroughbred season on Sept. 
12. 
</P>
<P>
To celebrate the opening, Los Alamitos will offer free general parking and 
general admission on Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
In a departure from other tracks conducting satellite wagering, the entire Los 
Alamitos facility will be open to the public during the Del Mar simulcast 
including the Turf Terrace dining room, the Cypress Room, and the 
newly-completed Finish Line Room, a nonsmoking area with table seating for up 
to 400. 
</P>
<P>
The Del Mar simulcast will continue through the opening weeks of the live 
harness meet at Los Alamitos, which begins Friday. Patrons attending the Del 
Mar simulcast during the day may stay for the night harness races at no extra 
charge. 
</P>
</TEXT>
